rmances from Ghana’s rapper Black Sherif, Psquare among other acts.  By Benjamin Njoku Afro fusion artiste, Burna Boy has made another history as he has been adjudged the overall Best Artiste in Africa. He also won Best Male Artiste from West Africa award. The hit maker, who few days ago was nominated for a Grammy award in the Best World… In "Entertainment" Barely a week after he won the Best African Act in this year’s edition of the MTV Europe Music Awards, EMA, Wizkid has made another history as he won three AFRIMA awards. In "Entertainment" 2019 was a good year for Nigerian music, both locally and internationally. Some awards were won and some were lost but all in all it was a fabulous year for Nigeria. Leading Nigerian artistes like Wizkid, Davido, Burna Boy, Tiwa Savage, Yemi Alade, Kizz Daniel and many others didn't disappoint… In "Entertainment"